18/03/2003
TIRANA, Albania -- On Monday (17 March), US President George W Bush expressed his country's gratitude for Albania's support in the global war against terrorism.
In a letter to Prime Minister Fatos Nano, Bush cited the support of Albanian troops to the international coalition forces in Afghanistan.
He added that Albania is an important factor to regional stability and pledged US support for the country's efforts to join NATO.
(Koha Jone, Zeri i Popullit - 18/03/03, ATA -17/03/03)
